description:
This one is more exclusive. This is art. This is satire.

This is one of the first "Art Satire" - Projects in the Cryptospace.

This "Alfons Trekner"-Collection shows the development from the Basic Alfons Trekner without many effects to the final picture wich has lots of artefacts and effects.

6 Steps - 6 beautiful unique pictures.

Check out the details of the final version!

The way of creation is the artists secret.

This is the second collection of our lovely Alfons Trekner. Others will follow. Maybe.
name: Alfons Trekner - The second collection
